name: Buoyancy Simulation
body:
### Welcome to the Page for the Buoyancy Simulation project
This project is what I am currently working on and leading at ITMS at URI. 

It involves trying to simulate buoyancy in an empty room with a balloon and air.

It is continuously being updated every Friday and is usually in developmental builds.

Some art done by coworkers.

To check it out...

[http://protein.mts.uri.edu/MPet/UnityProj/](http://protein.mts.uri.edu/MPet/UnityProj/)

```
Updates:

April 6, 2014
Removed unused files...
...which fixed Unity Editor crashes
Added an NPC
```
